Merges the values of two dictionaries, which are expected to be dictionaries, e.g
d1 = {'a': {'x': pqr}}
d2 = {'a': {'y': lmn}, 'b': {'y': rst}}
will return: {'a': {'x': pqr, 'y': lmn}, 'b': {'y': rst}}.
Collisions of the keys of the sub-dictionaries are not checked.

